  <!-- EN: The AC-8 Autocannon is a semi-automatic heavy weapon that fires APHET (Armor-Piercing High-Explosive Tracer) rounds. These specialized rounds deliver devastating penetration against armored targets while causing explosive damage upon impact. With its precision and destructive firepower, the AC-8 is a top-tier choice for Helldivers taking on heavily fortified enemies. -->
   
